{
  "name": "RPlog_Malign_and_the_Holocron",
  "title": "Malign and the Holocron",
  "summary": "In his opulent office aboard the Super Star Destroyer Malevolence, Grand Admiral Danik Kreldin broods over a Sith Holocron resting on his desk when the wounded Warlord Darth Malign pays an unannounced visit. Malign, his torso still bandaged from his exploits on Coruscant, levitates the Holocron into his own hand, an act that visibly irritates Kreldin and prompts a show of power that cows the Admiral's bodyguards Tibor and Sethas. Reminding Kreldin of their blood pact and his place in the Dark Brotherhood, Malign asserts his authority before the two settle into a wary conversation over Corellian ale. Their exchange reveals the uneasy alliance between the Sith and the ambitious Admiral, each pursuing his own ends. Malign departs with a parting reference to Ord Trasi, leaving Kreldin to his ambitions and the Holocron returned to its place.",
